OL,3,CWidow, 95, goes to court with scholar
OL,4,Cover washing in communal garden
OL,6,FMrs Grant said: "It's the principle.
OL,7,FIt is a very nice block of flats by
OL,8,Fthe suspension bridge.
OL,10,F"All the people crossing the bridge
OL,11,Fsee the washing.
OL,13,F"They could move them behind the
OL,14,Fgarages, away from the communal
OL,15,Fgardens and the lovely views."
