OL,3,CWidow, 95, goes to court with scholar
OL,4,Cover washing in communal garden
OL,6,FA second judge has now intervened in a
OL,7,Fbid to resolve a dispute. Judge Walsh
OL,8,Ftold the appeal hearing in Exeter: "It
OL,9,Fis an unusual case," and told the
OL,10,Fparties they need to reach a
OL,11,Fsettlement in the next three months.
OL,13,FHe warned the legal costs would be
OL,14,Fthousands of pounds for a "relatively
OL,15,Fminor matter".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
