OL,6,FMrs Grant's barrister Jonathan Ward
OL,7,Fsaid the earlier judgement was
OL,8,F"fatally flawed" and any changes made
OL,9,Fshould take into account good estate
OL,10,Fmanagement, be reasonable and made
OL,11,Fonly after proper consultation with
OL,12,Fall the leaseholders.
OL,14,FAfter the hearing Mrs Grant said: "I
OL,15,Fhave never hung my washing out and I
OL,16,Fhave been here since 1992. There are
OL,17,Fthree people who hang their washing
OL,18,Fout. It's not very nice.
